From 234518700047a32293db971397f79051d4e85b4c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ved <ved@localhost>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 19:46:40 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] Fix enum display, redistribute unsupported symbol
 capital, UI cleanup
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Strip alpaca-py enum prefixes (OrderSide.BUY → buy, OrderStatus.FILLED → filled)
- Add ALPACA_SUPPORTED_CRYPTO set; redistribute FTM/BNB/APE/MATIC capital
  to supported symbols so ~100% of equity deploys instead of ~65%
- Hide "API Keys Not Configured" banner when Alpaca is connected
- Color-code order status (filled=green, canceled=red, partial=amber)
- Show "No daily P&L data yet" notice on calendar instead of blank zeros
- Clean up Gantt timeline side matching for robustness

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
